  "title": "Automation Engineer (Siemens PLC / WinCC / SCADA)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Define work scope and specs for contractors</li>\n  <li>Handle PLC/HMI programming, control schematics, and single-line drawings</li>\n  <li>Support machine startup, testing, and troubleshooting</li>\n  <li>Assist with project execution and installations</li>\n  <li>Travel for overseas projects as needed</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Bachelor's Degree in Electrical, Electronic, or Mechatronic Engineering</li>\n  <li>3–5 years of automation experience</li>\n  <li>Skilled in Siemens PLC and WinCC programming</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of control panel design, schematics, and motor controls</li>\n  <li>Strong communication skills and ability to manage tasks independently</li>\n  <li>Willing to travel oversea to support at customers' sites</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If interested, please submit your application to cvs@jdawms.com with your expected salary and resume.</p>\n<p>We regret that only short-listed candidates will be contacted shortly. By submitting your application or resume, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and sharing of your personal information with potential employers for their assessment.</p>\n<p>JDA WMS Pte Ltd | EA Personnel: Pham Thi Tuyet Mai</p>\n<p>EA License No: 23S1595 | EA Registration No: R25127838</p>",
